#
      LYMPHATIC SUBTYPE.
@ﾄﾅﾒﾈ  : ﾎﾒ ﾐﾎﾆﾄﾅHﾈﾟ ﾄﾎ 18 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Inborn weakness of reticulo-endothelial system, the immunity is decreased especially at upper respiratory tracts disorders. The thymus function is decreased.
@ﾌﾎﾋﾎﾄﾛﾅ : ﾎﾒ 18 ﾄﾎ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Increased allergic readiness, the immunity to contagions is decreased, inclination to the stomach and duodenum diseases.
@ﾏﾎﾆﾈﾋﾛﾅ : ﾑﾒﾀﾐﾘﾅ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
The liver barrier function and intestine evacuation function are decreased, that causes metabolism type diseases.
#
      LYMPHATIC HYDROGENOUS SUBTYPE.
@ﾄﾅﾒﾈ  : ﾎﾒ ﾐﾎﾆﾄﾅHﾈﾟ ﾄﾎ 18 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Predisposition to the nasopharynx trabecular hyperplasia, adenoids formation, decreased anti-microbe resistivity of bronchi mucosa (inclination to infection-allergic inflammation processes in bronchi and upper respiratory tracts of exudative type predominantly). Inclination to tissue allergic reactions of deferred type (exudative diathesis, toxic-allergic dermatitis).
@ﾌﾎﾋﾎﾄﾛﾅ : ﾎﾒ 18 ﾄﾎ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Inclination (risk) to system autoimmune diseases after intercurrent infections (rheumatism, collagenosis, hepatitis).
@ﾏﾎﾆﾈﾋﾛﾅ : ﾑﾒﾀﾐﾘﾅ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Risk of diseases, concerned the violation of mineral metabolism or conjunctive tissue disorganization (arthrosis, spinal column osteochondrosis, urolithiasis).
#
      LYMPHATIC HYDROGENOUS SUBTYPE WITH SIGNS OF URATE DIATHESIS.
Violation of rheologic and colloid properties of biological liquids of organism. Inadequate selective reactivity of reticulo-endothelial system. Inclination to changes of antigen tissue properties and metabolism violation.
@ﾄﾅﾒﾈ  : ﾎﾒ ﾐﾎﾆﾄﾅHﾈﾟ ﾄﾎ 18 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Inclination to hyperplasia of lymphoid tissue, lymphadenopathy, diathesis, enuresis).
@ﾌﾎﾋﾎﾄﾛﾅ : ﾎﾒ 18 ﾄﾎ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Inclination to system autoimmune diseases (rheumatism, collagenosis, hyperplasia), adrenal incompetence and diseases, concerned the violation of protein-mineral metabolism (urolithiasis, cholelithiasis, spinal column osteochondrosis, arthritis).
@ﾏﾎﾆﾈﾋﾛﾅ : ﾑﾒﾀﾐﾘﾅ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Inclination to metabolic origin diseases (urolithiasis, cholelithiasis, arthrosis, spinal column osteochondrosis, mineral infiltration of major vessels walls)
#
      LYMPHATIC HYDROGENOUS SUBTYPE WITH SIGNS OF CHOLESTEROSIS.
Composition of redundant cholesterol utilization violation with changed reactivity of reticulo-endothelial system.
@ﾄﾅﾒﾈ  : ﾎﾒ ﾐﾎﾆﾄﾅHﾈﾟ ﾄﾎ 18 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Hyperlipoidemia and hypercholesterolemia with inclination to redundant body mass accumulation up to obesity. Decreased resistivity to intercurrent infections with adenoids formation, chronic tonsillitis.
@ﾌﾎﾋﾎﾄﾛﾅ : ﾎﾒ 18 ﾄﾎ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Skin infection resistivity decrease, sebaceous glands function violation and redundant cholesterol focal accumulation in subcutaneous fat. Early atherosclerosis risk.
@ﾏﾎﾆﾈﾋﾛﾅ : ﾑﾒﾀﾐﾘﾅ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Inclination to hypercholesterolemia, hyperlipoproteidemia of high density lipids. Target organs vessels atherosclerosis with corresponding clinical manifestations (ischemic heart disease, hypertension syndrome, cerebral vessel diseases, renovascular pathology). Metabolic vessels lesions, inclination to lithogenesis in biliferous and urinary tracts.
#
      LYMPHATIC NEUROGEN SUBTYPE.
High nervous system sensitivity with inclination to hyper-reaction to slight and moderate stress impacts. Inclination to lymphoid tissue hyperplasia.
@ﾄﾅﾒﾈ  : ﾎﾒ ﾐﾎﾆﾄﾅHﾈﾟ ﾄﾎ 18 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Inclination to tonsils hypertrophy, accessory nasal sinuses and middle ear inflammation. Increased emotionality and irritability, sometimes without external manifestations, which can lead to neurosis or difficulties of social adaptation.
@ﾌﾎﾋﾎﾄﾛﾅ : ﾎﾒ 18 ﾄﾎ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Possible decrease of tolerance to physical and psycho-emotional loadings, which lead to nervous exhaustion and irritable weakness, migraine type headaches.
Risk of manifestation of neurogenic bronchial asthma attacks, stress erosive gastritis, gastric and duodenum ulcer.   
@ﾏﾎﾆﾈﾋﾛﾅ : ﾑﾒﾀﾐﾘﾅ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Risk of essential hypertension, ischemic heart disease, violations of cerebral circulation, stomach and duodenum ulcer. The probability of metabolic violations in joints and spinal column is high.
#
      LYMPHATIC SUBTYPE WITH WEAKNESS OF CONNECTIVE (PERITONEUM) TISSUE.
Inborn friability and weakness of connective tissue and muscles of gastrointestinal tract on background of moderate increase of lymphoid tissue reaction.
@ﾄﾅﾒﾈ  : ﾎﾒ ﾐﾎﾆﾄﾅHﾈﾟ ﾄﾎ 18 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Inclination to fast organism allergisation, tonsils hypertrophy, appearance of intestinal syndrome at intercurrent infections. 
Risk of increase of drugs side effect on gastrointestinal tract. The use of food with irritant properties can lead to gastrointestinal tract mucosa inflammation. The peculiarities of connective tissue structure enlarge the risk of myopia development, pathologies of blood vessels and ligament-joint organism apparatus. 
@ﾌﾎﾋﾎﾄﾛﾅ : ﾎﾒ 18 ﾄﾎ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Risk of development of autoimmune diseases after the acute virus infections (collagenose). 
@ﾏﾎﾆﾈﾋﾛﾅ : ﾑﾒﾀﾐﾘﾅ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Probable disturbance of venous blood circulation (varicose phlebectasia, hemorrhoids) caused by inborn weakness of a valvural veins apparatus. Reduced tonus of digestive tract organs (digestive system) increases the probability of stomach pathology, gall bladder, pancreas and increase of autointoxication caused by slowed evacuation of intestinal contents.
The age changes of joint surfaces and ligament system of spinal column and big joints are accelerated with a tendency to limitation of their mobility. High risk of hernias development in physical loads.
#
      LYMPHATIC SUBTYPE WITH WEAKNESS OF CONNECTIVE (PANCREOTRIADE) TISSUE.
Inborn friability and instability of connective tissue of digestive glands stroma and mucous cover of respiratory tract on the background of moderate inclination to hyperplasia of lymphoid tissue. The risk of pancreas and bronchi diseases is increased.
@ﾄﾅﾒﾈ  : ﾎﾒ ﾐﾎﾆﾄﾅHﾈﾟ ﾄﾎ 18 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Susceptibility to catarrhal diseases is increased with tendency to tonsils hypertrophy and development of complications of the accessory nasal sinuses (antritis, sinusitis). The risk of transformation of acute respiratory tract diseases into chronic forms with forming of asthmoid component is increased. Inborn morphological heterogeneity of pancreas increases the risk of development of both exocrine (pancreatitis) and endocrine (diabetes mellitus) diseases of pancreas and formation of calcifications in the gland. Structural features of connective tissue of eyeball can cause early myopia. The violation of elasticity of vascular walls and ligament apparatus of spinal column and joints is possible.
@ﾌﾎﾋﾎﾄﾛﾅ : ﾎﾒ 18 ﾄﾎ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Risk of development of auto-immune diseases (collagenosis, rheumatic disease) and myopia progression is present. The tendency of transferring of respiratory tract acute diseases into chronic and association of asthmatic component. Increase of morphological heterogeneity of a pancreas with risk of formation of calcifications and fibrosis. Decrease of tolerance to glucose with probable disturbance of carbohydrate metabolism. The elasticity of blood vessels walls is decreased. Taking alcohol can cause pancreatitis.
@ﾏﾎﾆﾈﾋﾛﾅ : ﾑﾒﾀﾐﾘﾅ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Present diseases of bronchi-lungs system are inclined to progression with development of a pneumosclerosis and emphysema of lungs. Overload of the right heart and respiratory failure are increasing. Secretory insufficiency of pancreas aggravates the process of digestion.
#
      LYMPHATIC SUBTYPE WITH WEAKNESS OF CONNECTIVE (CARDIORENAL) TISSUE.
Inborn weakness of connective tissue, the lymphocytic barrier is weakened. Inclination to heart and kidneys diseases, frequently of autoimmune type.
@ﾄﾅﾒﾈ  : ﾎﾒ ﾐﾎﾆﾄﾅHﾈﾟ ﾄﾎ 18 ﾋﾅﾒ.
The weakness of lymphocytic barrier causes the diseases of upper respiratory paths and accessory nasal sinuses. The sluggish diseases in a zone of lymphoid ring with symptoms of mucous hyperplasia are typical. Delayed treatment causes the development of rhematoid processes with injury of cardiac valves. Early myopia and astigmatism are typical. Chronic course of respiratory infections is frequently complicated by renal pathology.
@ﾌﾎﾋﾎﾄﾛﾅ : ﾎﾒ 18 ﾄﾎ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Probability of autoimmune reactions, flaccid rheumatoid diseases are high. Early myopia is present or progressing. Development of renal hypertension is possible. Weakness of ligaments of spinal column can result into pathology of radicular type. Weakness of a valves leads to possible congestion in lower extremities.
@ﾏﾎﾆﾈﾋﾛﾅ : ﾑﾒﾀﾐﾘﾅ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Predisposition to arterial hypertension of mixed genesis, decrease and disturbance of coronary circulation, urolithiasis.
#
      LYMPHATIC SUBTYPE WITH WEAKNESS OF CONNECTIVE (BRONCHOPULMONARY) TISSUE.
