Exudative processes in upper respiratory paths mucous cover are increased, the nasal respiration is elaborated. Development of chronic diseases of respiratory paths, frequently with asthmatic component, is possible. Weakness of connective tissue can cause early myopia, arcuation of spinal column, specially in upper-thoracic departments.
@ﾌﾎﾋﾎﾄﾛﾅ : ﾎﾒ 18 ﾄﾎ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Inborn inclination to bronchospastic reaction can lead to bronchial asthma, chronic bronchites, professional lungs diseases, overload of right heart. Smoking is heightened risk factor. Radiculites with  radicular syndromes are probable due to the weakness of ligamental-joints system of spinal column.
@ﾏﾎﾆﾈﾋﾛﾅ : ﾑﾒﾀﾐﾘﾅ 50 ﾋﾅﾒ.
Chronic processes in bronchi and lungs, symptoms of secondary morphological changes of pulmonary tissue, overload of right heart, ventilation of lungs is decreased.
